        <updateDate>2022-08-11T13:18:07Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Safe Travel Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires proof of COVID-19 vaccinations or proof of negative COVID-19 test results for passengers on planes and Amtrak trains; patrons of airports; and employees, contractors, and subcontractors of air carriers, airports, and Amtrak.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
